description: Retrieves a list that describes modifications to the configuration of Bring Your Own License (BYOL) for the specified account.

nested_items.name: AccountModifications
nested_items.description: The list of modifications to the configuration of BYOL.

nested_items.name: ModificationState
nested_items.description: The state of the modification to the configuration of BYOL.

nested_items.name: DedicatedTenancySupport
nested_items.description: The status of BYOL (whether BYOL is being enabled or disabled).

nested_items.name: DedicatedTenancyManagementCidrRange
nested_items.description: The IP address range, specified as an IPv4 CIDR block, for the management network interface used for the account.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the modification of the BYOL configuration was started.

nested_items.name: ErrorCode
nested_items.description: The error code that is returned if the configuration of BYOL cannot be modified.

nested_items.name: ErrorMessage
nested_items.description: The text of the error message that is returned if the configuration of BYOL cannot be modified.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to use to retrieve the next page of results. This value is null when there are no more results to return.
